1. *Verujete* li da ću uspeti? (Do you believe I will succeed?)
2. Oni *veruju* u uspeh. (They believe in success.)
3. *Verovali* smo da je to moguće. (We believed that it was possible.)
4. *Verovao* je da će uspeti. (He believed he would succeed.)
5. Oni *veruju* da je to istina. (They believe that it is true.)